Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:18.31,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:29.77,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:36.70,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:47.83,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:56.76,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:01:08.65,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:20.54,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:26.38,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:36.18,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:29.77,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:36.70,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:47.83,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:56.76,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:01:08.65,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:20.54,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:26.38,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:36.18,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:47.37,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(100,110)}Ep. 13 - Ben Has Arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:10.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come out, Sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:13.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sticky? Sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:18.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you go, Sticky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:20.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:22.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:25.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen\Nto the goat, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.03,0:02:29.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sticky has disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:32.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:34.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She probably already had a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:35.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That must be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:39.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we prepared just the place for her\Nto have a baby, laid down all that grass there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:41.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where else could she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:43.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, we should find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.59,0:02:44.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:46.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You start there, near Mrs. Mac's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:49.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll go check behind,\Nall the way to the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:54.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.53,0:02:55.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:58.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May, what's all this yelling\Nso early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:03:02.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sticky disappeared! And I thought her baby goat\Nis supposed to be born today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:03.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:05.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then help me look for her, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:06.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Clara, you go search as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:10.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Father, just where in the world\Ncould a goat go to give birth?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:13.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It can do it wherever.\NIt just gotta be someplace safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:16.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Which means she wasn't comfortable in that tent?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:19.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,With two girls were sleeping there\Nin front of her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:20.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Might be the case, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:26.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sticky? Sticky!\NStop hiding and come out, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sticky! Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:35.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me she was feeling thirsty\Nand went to the river again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:36.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:54.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:58.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sticky! Where are you?\NCome out please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.71,0:04:06.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Mr. Pettywell brought along this dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:12.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It'd better not be that you\Ntried to take a bite of our Sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:17.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, here! Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:18.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The babies are born!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:19.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:23.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come quickly! There are three of them!\NThree babies are born!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:37.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:38.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Keep trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:55.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did it!
Comment: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:58.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:20.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, it's almost time for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:21.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:42.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May, what's going on?\NAre you fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, and this feels good!
Comment: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:55.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:57.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:06:00.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dem-zuckin-ma-vingers-beelz-zdrange\Nbud-zdill-good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:12.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come near here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:25.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When there's nobody around,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:28.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Pettywell's dog might try\Nto make a move on Sticky and her babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:32.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But think of it, Kate. The dog doesn't have any reason\Nto do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That dog will find a reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:37.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at any rate, once we're done with the breakfast,\NI'll make an enclosure for the goats.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:39.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:41.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go relieve Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are your plans for today after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:52.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? I'll ask around if there's any oxcart for hire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:55.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We need to hurry with getting Ben\Nand our luggage to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:58.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I wonder if Ben\Nis managing all right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:25.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, make way, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:42.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well now, do you plan to stay inside there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've finished already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:45.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:55.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This way, they'll always be safe, Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:56.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:58.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To build something like that with a breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:07:59.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,True!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:05.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Remember when he promised to make that house\Nbig one day? I bet, it'll be just as easy for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:07.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It totally will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:25.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Could those be the prefabricated home materials?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning to you, Mr. Popple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:33.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:37.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Am I correct in saying those are the prefabricated home\Nmaterials you brought with you from England?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:42.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Precisely so.\NHowever, I no longer have anything to do with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:49.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was hoping to procure an oxcart,\None way or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:52.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We never have enough oxen and horses\Nto pull the cars here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:53.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:55.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:57.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You need to find me a skilled carpenter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:09:00.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If he's already busy with other job,\Ntell him I'll pay him twice the usual rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:01.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:03.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Leave immediately, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:03.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:09.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you won't have to go anywhere at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:11.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Good Morning, Popple!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Mr. Pettywell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:16.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Have you changed you mind,\Nby any chance, Mr. Popple?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:17.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,On which matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:21.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, about assembling\Nthat prefabricated home, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:23.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:25.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I heard you.\NHow much do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:27.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Name your price, loud and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:29.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:31.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:34.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I refuse to do\Nany house-assembling work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:36.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:40.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I already have my hands full\Nof my own house matters that I need to tend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:41.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:51.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How can you do that to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After this, I'm heading to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.19,0:10:03.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How is your sister's husband looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:05.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The fever just won't subside, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:08.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We definitely need to have a doctor examine him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you find one soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:12.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But that doctor doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:16.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Many things like oxen and horses are sparse here,\Nbut the doctors are the sparsest of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:25.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. I think it's best that we load this one first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:27.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:36.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I see the loading is almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:40.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How does it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:44.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Am I going to have to walk all the way to Adelaide\Nby myself, or is there a vacant seat, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:50.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well as long as your hindquarters are sturdy enough,\NI'm sure we'll find some spot to seat you at.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:52.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If my hindquarters end up a bit sore,\Nthen so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:55.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean to be nagging,\Nbut doctor, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:56.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:59.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,About staying to live in Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:02.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aye. My mind is made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:03.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:05.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:08.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure, my tardiness to the ship\Nwas the manifestation of Lord's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'd like to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:14.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,All right! In that case, doctor,\Nlet me take care of the rest for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Take care of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:20.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,For you, doctor,\NI can build a magnificent clinic in Adelaide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:21.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:26.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. Because I'm such a shrewd merchant,\Nmy undertakings never end up being unprofitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:29.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No proper doctors here\Nfor thousands of miles around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:33.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If we open a clinic in the middle of it,\Nthere would be lines upon lines of patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:36.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We could even get away\Nwith charging a little extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:38.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say if you and me\Nhalve the profits?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:40.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:43.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:43.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:47.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't become a doctor to make money from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:50.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you need the money\Nto buy the booze that you love so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:54.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally. And I'm fine\Nwith being paid just a smidgen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:55.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just a smidgen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:12:00.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. But at any rate,\Nplease don't forget about what I proposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:01.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:04.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And thanks a lot for letting me\Nstay at your place yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:07.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, are you ready to set out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:10.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm sure we'll surprise dad a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:14.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm. I bet he never managed\Nto scout another oxcart in Adelaide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:17.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's only thanks to you that we scouted this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:20.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. That's because of my natural knack\Nfor making deals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:23.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what am I saying?\NIt's lies, all lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:26.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I scouted this oxcart purely by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:30.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, one way or another, we should just be glad\Nyou'll reunite with your family soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:31.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:34.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Doctor,\Nplease get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:36.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Okay-okay-okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:37.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He-he.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Here? Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:47.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for looking after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:48.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Mr. Parker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:51.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, take care now.\NGive my regards to your dad and mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:54.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And tell them, I'll also be coming\Nto Adelaide one of these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:55.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:01.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And say hello from me\Nto children as well, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:03.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, 'kay, 'kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate! Lucy-May!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:32.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate! Lucy-May!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:36.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:46.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate! Lucy-May!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:47.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:52.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot, what'll we do if she finds us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:05.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:06.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:07.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:11.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When I gave then the list of tasks I got for them,\Ngirls ran off for somewhere, looking appalled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:14.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They're just hopeless.\NWell, so be it. We'll do it as two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:17.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right. So how does it look?\NCan still use that stove?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:19.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't seem to have anything wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:22.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, want me to boil some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:24.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We can do that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:26.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,First, let's arrange the dinnerware\Nin the right order.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:30.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,With this, we'll be able to cook inside the house\Nfor the first time in ages, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:33.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But that sure is a cramped kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:35.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to miss\Nthe kitchen we had back in England.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:38.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, it's a bit late to be saying that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:41.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.\NWell, let's take the dinnerware out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:44.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We should be allowed that,\Nonce in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:47.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Since our arrival to Australia,\Nwe're only ever being given a list of tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:50.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Let's play away the rest\Nof today, without rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:56.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Anything is fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:58.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You should be the one choosing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:14:59.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You choose, Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:06.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help wondering what was it\NClara was calling us for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:10.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, obviously, it was to give us\Nsome new list of tasks, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:12.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Must be you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:21.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You were the one who proposed running away before Clara gives us a list of tasks, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:22.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:26.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But now, having pulled off\Nsuch a successful escape, what should we play?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:28.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? You got something you wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:30.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's for you to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:32.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:34.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we're returning, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:38.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:54.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And here it's just the two of us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:55.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not having a lot of friends is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:58.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Think they'll ever let us join in the fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:01.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That girl is so good at climbing trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:08.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She seems very determined,\Ndespite being a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:10.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can probably do that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:13.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Being just two is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:17.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,True. Hide-and-seek and even tag\Nare both boring when played by just two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:20.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do we stop playing, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.01,0:16:20.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:25.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I still wonder why was Clara\Ncalling us back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:27.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:36.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom and Clara have their hands full of work\Nbecause we've just finished moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:40.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll feel bad for it later,\Nif we don't try to help at least a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So we ended up doing exactly that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:44.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:45.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:50.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It might just be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:54.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We need to hurry, Kate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:55.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:08.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, wouldn't it be best\Nto take out the firewood that's so damp?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:08.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:12.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:15.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This won't do!\NWe've got Tob sleeping over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:18.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take him outside now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Clara, is it a fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:35.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you two been\Nall that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Went to the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:39.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But more importantly,\Nwhat's with all that smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.11,0:17:43.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong with the stove.\NThe chimney won't draw out any smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There must be something stuck inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:49.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The chimney is clogged...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:52.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Clara, where's mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:54.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah! Still in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:59.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The two of you stay out.\NI need you to look after Tob.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:06.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The chimney looks completely clogged.\NBarely any smoke is coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:07.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:13.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It looks as though there is some draw, but the smoke\Nis actually returning into the room through a crack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:18.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid it will be easier to rebuild this house\Nfrom ground-up than to repair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:19.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:43.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is it just me, or is our house\Nshrouded in smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:46.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? A fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:02.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A bump?! Can't hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:02.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Comment: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:05.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:06.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:07.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ouch! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:08.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:10.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.20,0:19:12.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, it ain't my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, it's the leg, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:14.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:18.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ouch! Ouch! Ouch! Ouch!\NAt this rate, I guess, it might even be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:20.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ouch! Ouch! Up now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:23.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're a doctor, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:26.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of guessing, won't you know for sure\Nonce you examine it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:29.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as much as I would've liked to,\Nit hurts to even touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:31.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ouch-ouch! See?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:34.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's nothing worth fretting over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:38.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... Ouch! Ouch! Ouch!\NHurts-hurts-hurts! Hurts bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:42.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:43.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is it broken after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:47.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, apparently, it was all right all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:50.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.\NWe're almost in Adelaide, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:52.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:07.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the house was more busted\Nthan what I liked to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:09.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to do something\Nabout the stove, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:13.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. At any rate,\Nit'll require a fundamental repair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:16.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If I do it with Ben's help,\Nit wouldn't take all that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Probably, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:19.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't get Ben to come here any time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:23.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you've found an oxcart\Nto carry the rest of our things here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:26.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Not really.\NI don't seem to find a single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:29.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, for how long will Ben\Nhave to stay over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:31.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:34.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Which means we can't start the repairs\Nany time soon either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:37.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're in trouble, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:51.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:05.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta think of the names for the babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:06.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You go think of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:08.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:12.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What you want to be called, little one? Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:16.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:22.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, aren't those darn heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:23.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.29,0:21:25.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Popple.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:27.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you're back already?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:28.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Popple.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:33.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Although I've just returned,\NI have a favor to ask already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:35.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If there's something I can do, I will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:39.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to accompany me\Nto Carrington Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:42.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To Carrington Street? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.14,0:21:43.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My brother-in-law is getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:47.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I want to show him to a doctor,\Nwho lives on Carrington Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.17,0:21:50.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can't that doctor come here instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:53.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.\NPeople come to see him from far and wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:57.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.\NHow do you intend to carry him there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:01.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I figured me and you\Ncould carry him on our backs by turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.70,0:22:04.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I guess our hands are tied,\Nsince it's our only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.70,0:22:06.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.48,0:22:10.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:13.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.87,0:22:16.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ben's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.18,0:22:22.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.14,0:22:25.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally come! You're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:29.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He managed to scout an oxcart by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.22,0:22:31.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! But for now, Mr. Bernard,\Nlet's make haste.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.51,0:22:32.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:35.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we use that oxcart\Nto carry the patient there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.59,0:22:39.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I brought the rest of our things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:42.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good work with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.95,0:22:45.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But for now, Ben,\Nwe've got a patient here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.78,0:22:48.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can we lend that oxcart for a bit longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.00,0:22:50.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We need to find something\Nto carry him to the doctor with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:54.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'll be alright for you to lend it.\NBut if you need a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:22:58.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Howdy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.11,0:22:59.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Deighton?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:02.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Popple.\NMy throat is as dry as a desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.97,0:23:06.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping you've got\Nsome booze at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.12,0:23:11.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Deighton, truly, you couldn't\Nhave come at a better time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:13.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? You {\i1}do{\i0} have some booze?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.50,0:23:18.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, mark my words, it's an opportune time\Nfor you to come to our place. Bernard, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:20.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? So you have it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:25.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bernard, this man is Doctor Deighton.\NHe's one hell of a doctor if I do say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.77,0:23:27.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Well, it's an honor...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:32.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thanks. But I'd still like to remind you,\Nmy throat is as dry as a desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.28,0:23:35.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is it in your house\Nwhere they got some booze, young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.41,0:23:49.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It was unimaginable to us\Nthat we'll get reunited with our brother so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.16,0:23:50.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It was the most delighting news.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.85,0:23:56.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, bringing along Dr. Deighton\Nwas really well-thought out of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.59,0:24:07.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,While returning from my trip for firewood,\NI ran into Mr. Heracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:10.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I felt obliged to thank him\Nfor saving my life the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.36,0:24:14.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Lucy-May of the Southern Rainbow:\N"A Stout Man".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.59,0:24:15.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
